    "7305215": {
        "Desc": "Go to the area near the ruins together with Tirzad",
        "Step": "According to what Jeht said, there may be a clue in the ruins that will get everyone out of this mess. Explore with caution.",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "We're here! Tirzad decided to come exploring with us."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "What now? You mean that researcher actually changed his mind?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "Ugh..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jebrael",
                    "T": "He knows the pros and cons, so naturally, he came along."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "All right, well, you'll get the chance to show off your skills soon enough! How should we enter the interior of the ruins? This is a researcher's specialty, right?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "This should be a piece of cake for you, right, Tirzad?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "O—Of course! I might be an Indoorsology researcher, but something as basic as this can't be too different from what's written in the books..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "Watch this!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "...Hmm, this is... There! That should do it..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Whoa, the door really opened!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Well, that's Mr. Tirzad for you!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "Heh, that's what sets us professionals apart from the amateurs."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Paimon wonders what it's like inside. Let's go in and take a look!"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
