    "7305236": {
        "Desc": "Leave the pit through the exit",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "I can feel a breeze... The exit must be close by! Keep looking. We'll be out of here in no time."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Woohoo! We can finally leave!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "...Although it's certain to be nothing but sand for miles around out there."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "At least we'll be able to see the sky."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "That's true!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "Where... Where do you guys get all that energy from? First it's exploring, then it's fighting... Let's slow down a little..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "You and father are the same age, aren't you, Tirzad? How many times have we stopped to rest so far?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "The mind of a child, the body of an old man... Geez."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Benben",
                    "T": "Beep beep... Bee-eep."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "I told you, I'm an Indoor... forget it. I'm the employer, so just listen to me!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "???",
                    "T": "Everyone rests with Tirzad for a while."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Oh? If it isn't Nachtigal!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nachtigal",
                    "T": "There you are. When the door on the other side suddenly opened, I knew you'd found an exit. I brought Cyrus and the others over."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Wow, that was pretty brave of you! What if it wasn't a shortcut at all, but a trap?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nachtigal",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nachtigal",
                    "T": "Heh, you've got a point."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "You mean that it didn't even occur to you?!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nachtigal",
                    "T": "Well, everything worked out fine in the end. We've reunited, haven't we? That's enough. By the way, we've got a new member here? That's great!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "That's a free Mondstadter for you."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "But it's better to be cautious at times like this!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "But isn't it great that we don't have to double back to rendezvous? Now we can find the exit together!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jebrael",
                    "T": "Follow the wind and find your way out. But don't let your guard down."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Okay... got it!"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
