    "7305223": {
        "Desc": "",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Father, I brought another new friend back! Look, this is the friend we just met, its name is Benben."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Benben",
                    "T": "Beep."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Oh, Tirzad's awake. Looks like things are going well with father."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "I don't know how you came to that ridiculous conclusion, but... let's not discuss that for now. What I'm most concerned about now is, what is that thing?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Didn't I just introduce you? This is our new friend, Benben."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "This doesn't seem like something that could be classified as a \"friend,\" could it?! Doesn't this look a little like the same thing that just attacked us?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "You don't have a lot of friends, do you, Tirzad?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "No, I don't... Wait, what does that have to do with this?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "You're way too uptight! You just need an open mind, and you'll be swimming in friends in no time. Isn't that right, Benben?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Benben",
                    "T": "Beep."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "And you're too lax!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "So, you don't know what Benben is either, huh?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "It... must be related to the guards here. I don't know exactly how to operate it, though."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "But this unique model doesn't attack outsiders and can even communicate to a certain extent... I don't remember reading anything about this."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Tirzad!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "Wh—What is it?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Isn't that amazing news?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "This is the \"material that no one has worked on before.\""
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "...?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "Wait a minute, could it be? No, it's too early to celebrate just yet... Maybe I was too narrow-minded and just happened to not see any relevant prior research on it..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "Maybe someone has already published ten treatises and thoroughly studied Benben's genealogy..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Why does this guy always jump to the worst conclusions..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jebrael",
                    "T": "Wait a minute, something doesn't seem right about it."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Benben",
                    "T": "Beep... Beep..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "What is it, Benben? Are you—"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Ooh! Benben seems to be reacting to Tirzad's stone slate!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jebrael",
                    "T": "Tirzad, pick the stone slate up and walk towards Benben."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "I hired you! Don't tell me what to do..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Whoa..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Ooh, Benben! You're amazing, Benben!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Benben",
                    "T": "Bee-eep. Beep!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Benben",
                    "T": "Beep-boop... Beep, Bee-eep!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Paimon doesn't completely understand what it's saying, but it seems happy!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "A small portion of the slate lit up. What does it mean? Do you have any idea, Tirzad?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "Hmm... It's hard to say, only a portion was lit up. Besides, I've told you all before..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Rigor is key to academic research, and you don't want to jump to conclusions, right?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "O—Oh, yes, that's true."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Heh, looks like we'll just have to find a way to light up the rest of the stone slate. Right, Benben?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Benben",
                    "T": "Beep... Bee-eep."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "#Hold on, I have a serious request to make of you, {NICKNAME}."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "Ahem, this has nothing to do with Jebrael or Jeht, so I kindly ask that you give us some space."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Huh? You gonna reveal some kind of secret? C'mon, I wanna hear it, too!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jebrael",
                    "T": "Jeht, mind your own business."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "But father, we're all companions here. Doesn't that make it our business?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jebrael",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Fine! I'll give you all the space you want. Let's go, Benben."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Benben",
                    "T": "Beep."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "7305241": {
        "Desc": "",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Hey, are you done whispering to each other yet?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jebrael",
                    "T": "Tirzad's ready to set off now. We should find an exit as soon as possible."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "I don't need you to speak for me. Um... That said, I am indeed ready to set off whenever."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Great! It's been a productive day, and I've got a feeling that we'll find a way out in no time! Benben and I will go on ahead. Everyone else can follow us."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Jeht and Benben sure have hit it off. That's... good, right?"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
