    "7305325": {
        "Desc": "",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Jebrael",
                    "T": "What is it?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "It isn't anything important..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Whose gravestone is this?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jebrael",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jebrael",
                    "T": "Who knows. Maybe it belongs to a nameless researcher who once tried their luck like Tirzad, but didn't roll high like he did."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jebrael",
                    "T": "King Deshret's secrets rarely reveal themselves to mortals."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jebrael",
                    "T": "Tirzad gave you the stone slate, right?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Uh, how did you know?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jebrael",
                    "T": "Keep it safe."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Is it important?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jebrael",
                    "T": "You can't be unaware of its value, surely?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Well, its value to whom?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jebrael",
                    "T": "...To our employer, of course. After all, he is depending on it to write his paper."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jebrael",
                    "T": "Anyway, let's head back. We shouldn't keep Jeht and the others waiting for too long."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
