    "7305318": {
        "Desc": "Explore the lower level of Khemenu Temple",
        "Talk": []
    },
    "7305319": {
        "Desc": "",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "Ugh, I'm exhausted. Moreover, besides Benben, we haven't made any other discoveries, and that makes my exhaustion all the worse for it."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Huh? This place is huge, and we've seen so much on the way here! Paimon's sure there's a lot to write about, right? Even if Paimon doesn't really know much about these things..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "Neither of you are a researcher, so of course you don't understand. What we've witnessed this whole time can only be considered as proof for existing research, except Benben..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "How should I explain this to a non-researcher...?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "Let me put it like this: I want my paper to get approved by the Akademiya's review... It's like love!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "What does this have to do with love?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "Let me explain!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Your lover is academic research?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "The current situation is that I want to love it, but it seems to hold no interest toward me."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "Ahem! A paper must stand out to pass the review. Just imagine that you're pursuing your ideal partner. If you're no different from the other candidates, then how will you capture their heart?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "This analogy sounds like a real stretch, y'know..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "The way Tirzad thinks is really strange. In my opinion, a couple just has to consider each other suitable. There's no need to compete with others."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "We're still talking about academic reviews, aren't we?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "Ugh... I shouldn't have made that example. Just forget what I said!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jebrael",
                    "T": "I guess this is where our little chat ends. It'll be more efficient if we split up and look for clues."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "An archaeological expedition with no hope in sight. *sigh* Who cares about efficiency?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jebrael",
                    "T": "That stone slate has lit up once. We'll definitely find a way to make it light up completely. We just have to not give up."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "But how can you guarantee that? Wait, so you really do know something, don't you?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jebrael",
                    "T": "What I do know is that there may be hope if we continue forward, but we'll leave empty-handed if we turn back now."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "Well... That is true."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Tirzad, stop worrying about this and that. An Indoorsology researcher like you has finally gotten the opportunity to enter some ruins, so just treat it as a chance to view some of your seniors' research subjects for yourself."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "#...You're right. I should be more professional. But even if we're going to split up, I want {NICKNAME} to stay close to me!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Okay..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "I'll have nothing to worry about with you around."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I want to explore freely too, you know..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "Then we'll explore freely together!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "#Haha! There's no danger here! And while you might be a researcher, you're terrible at puzzles. You'll just be a burden to {NICKNAME}."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "Exploring ruins has never been my forte! But if I'm given enough time... And pen and paper! Then such problems will be no problem at all!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Alright, alright. Anyway, just shout \"help meeee!\" if you're in danger or something..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "One of us will get there in time. Probably."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "What if none of you do?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "It's as impossible as breaking open ten bad eggs in a row for breakfast."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "I think you need some lessons in mathematics, Jeht... I can introduce a teacher to you once we return."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "7305313": {
        "Desc": "Return to the previous room and look for clues",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "That's strange! What's a ship doing in here?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Might it make sense because this is an \"ocean of sand\"?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "Perhaps a river used to flow through here, but it dried up? Or perhaps... this boat was not made to be used by the living?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "I'll have to head back and do some research on the geographical changes here to confirm my theory..."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
