    "7305321": {
        "Desc": "",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "Great! As expected of my assistant! No mechanism or puzzle shall ever be your match!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "No need to exaggerate..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "#{NICKNAME} is impressive, but you should help out too, Tirzad!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Speaking of which, didn't you complain about being exhausted and not discovering anything so far? How are you this motivated now?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "Ahem! It's because my researcher's intuition tells me that we're about to make a breakthrough!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "...Researcher's intuition?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Is it like an adventurer's instinct?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Oh! Paimon gets it! That's the ability to predict that there will be an ambush at the corner or a trap behind a door, right?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "#Then you'd better be careful, {NICKNAME}. Father, let's prepare for battle as well."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "What are all of you talking about? The researcher's intuition I mentioned is based on vast knowledge and careful observation. It's akin to a flash of genius!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "But what you've said does make sense. My consideration is lacking in that aspect. Well, if there's danger... I'll be counting on all of you to do the jobs I hired you for, then."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
