    "7305438": {
        "Desc": "Ride the elevator",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Paimon feels even smaller now that we've gotten closer... Paimon feels as insignificant as a grain of sand..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "That was also one of King Deshret's means of ruling. Building huge spectacles to instill the idea that his subjects are small and insignificant into them, thus achieving the objective of domesticating them."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "The act of using huge amounts of manpower to build such a spectacle in the desert is a testament to King Deshret's tyranny."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Benben",
                    "T": "Beep... Beep... Bee-eep beep..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Whoa! So Benben can even open a door this huge?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "It's difficult to say! Maybe it just opened on its own! It may... it might have nothing to do with Benben."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Gah, why's he being so stubborn?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "Then explain to me how this thing... Benben opened the door. What's the logic behind that?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hmm... Paimon doesn't know either!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Hmm, Benben? What is it? Do you want to go inside? Is there something you're familiar with in there?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Benben",
                    "T": "Beep... Beep..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jebrael",
                    "T": "A grain of sand is insignificant, but an ocean of them possesses immeasurable strength. Researcher of blind faith, do you really have the courage to set foot into the sands?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "We're already here! So of course we must go inside!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "Still, my researcher's intuition is telling me that the danger ahead is incomparable to the dangers we've faced so far!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "#I doubt I can trust either of you desert dwellers, so {NICKNAME}, I'm counting on you to keep me safe!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Come on, it's just some differences of opinion. It isn't that serious, is it?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "Hmph! You don't get it at all! A collision of views in academics is no different from a battle!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Sheesh, this guy's really getting more annoying by the minute!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "So, are all of you done? It's not that easy to hold Benben back..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Sorry."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "So, Benben really wants to go inside, huh? Let's stop delaying then."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "7305402": {
        "Desc": "",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Wow! These ruins are magnificent!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "Those aren't ordinary ruins. If the records are correct, they should be King Deshret's Mausoleum. It's where the tyrant is buried."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Uh... Sh—should we still go forward, then?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jebrael",
                    "T": "All questions have an answer, and all answers slumber here."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "Hmph! I will do this, even if all I achieve is showing some ignorant mercenaries the error of their ways..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "#Uh... {NICKNAME}, let's head over carefully!"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "7305403": {
        "Desc": "Go to the Mausoleum of King Deshret",
        "Step": "Going through the passage in Khemenu Temple, Tirzad and Jebrael made it to another set of ruins, which are yet more majestic. The trouble is that they're still not getting along with each other... One can only hope that further exploration will go more smoothly...",
        "Talk": []
    },
    "7305439": {
        "Desc": "",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "#{NICKNAME}! Hey, {NICKNAME}!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "What happened?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Oh, thank goodness! You're finally awake!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Uh, Paimon doesn't know what happened either. We were here when Paimon woke up. Maybe it was a trap?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "...Anyway, let's go look for the others!"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
