    "7305422": {
        "Desc": "",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "*sob* You're finally here! My savior!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "I woke up to find myself in this place, and my whole body felt like it was falling apart..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "That wasn't even the end of it! I went to great lengths to finally find Jeht and her father, but the Fatui attacked again!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Whoa! That's terrible!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "#Paimon, {NICKNAME}, did you see Benben on the way? B—Benben is gone! I searched all around the area to no avail..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "#We didn't, did we, {NICKNAME}?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "We didn't."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Then... Benben must be up ahead. It's the only one left alone now, so we must find it soon!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "There's no need to be so anxious. The way I see it, it probably only got lost because it likes running off by itself so much."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Benben has helped us so much! It's part of our group! I don't know about you, but I wouldn't be so cruel as to abandon a companion!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "I must find Benben..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jebrael",
                    "T": "Its capabilities are undeniable, Tirzad. I'm sure you're aware of that."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "Even you, Jebrael...?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "Fine, you win! Let's find Benben first. But... I'm leaving if we encounter the Fatui again!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Speaking of which, what are the Fatui doing here? Is this some kind of archaeological hotspot?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "Huh? That's impossible! I wouldn't have chosen this place if it were such a hot research topic."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "True. After all, you've said yourself that you aren't a very great researcher."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "You probably wouldn't stand a chance against those elites!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "Hey! It's called avoiding battles where victory isn't guaranteed."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jebrael",
                    "T": "Either way, this place may be more troublesome than we expected. Let's advance carefully."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
