    "7305420": {
        "Desc": "",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "That room's... I wonder if it was a trap. Why did it send us here?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "It's common practice to attempt to expel trespassing outsiders. If you want technical details, you'll have to wait until I return and ask some Kshahrewar experts..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Oh, but I wonder: If King Deshret was a tyrant like you say, why wasn't that a lethal mechanism instead?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "We're just lucky that we haven't encountered one yet! And I hope that we never do..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "Look! We can continue our expedition on this path. I don't want to give up when we've finally found some clues about the stone slate."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jebrael",
                    "T": "Shh... Those guys down there aren't friendly. We must find a way around them to proceed forward, or..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "#It's the Fatui and the Eremites again! Y'know, {NICKNAME}, Paimon's been thinking... Did they kidnap Benben?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "We've got to rescue it!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jebrael",
                    "T": "Jeht! Calm down."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "Are you kidding? I'm just an ordinary researcher. I've come here to solve academic problems, not to fight!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "But we wouldn't have been able to get here without Benben... And Tirzad, you'll never be able to solve those academic problems of yours without Benben, either!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "#That's right! We've got to rescue it, even if it's just for the sake of completing our expedition! You're not afraid of them, right, {NICKNAME}?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "#Don't worry, {NICKNAME}'s an expert at dealing with the Fatui! But we should still be careful!"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "7305436": {
        "Desc": "Investigate the room located deep within",
        "Talk": []
    },
    "7305437": {
        "Desc": "",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "This should be the last place..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "#{NICKNAME}, let's take a look at the stone slate. If things go the same way as before, there may be clues about the stone slate here."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "This is..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "It lit up as expected, and... there's a map?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Tirzad, these symbols on the stone slate should be your area of expertise, right? So, isn't it time to give us an explanation?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "Yes, these inscriptions are most likely texts of praise. Someone in an exalted position like King Deshret would naturally be fond of things like this."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "Look! All these wonders are an attempt at whitewashing his rule."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Whitewashing, you say... But Paimon remembers you saying something different earlier!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "\"Rule by force,\" you said!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Exactly! You spoke of submission and terror before — and you sure sounded convinced then, too!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "Wh—What do you mean? These are conclusions I came to after careful analysis and reasoning. Just look at it! What would it be if not an attempt at whitewashing?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "It's very common for rulers to sugar-coat all their deeds. Since this entire ruin was made by King Deshret, it's not that hard to imagine that this is its purpose, right?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "Reflecting on your own shortcomings in your work... Well, we researchers do that."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "Though they mostly just write a few hypocritical lines in the acknowledgments of a research paper and call it a day."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "And you know what? They're just pretending to be modest. Why would any academic really believe that they're incompetent, anyway?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "#{NICKNAME}, somehow Paimon gets the feeling that he's hurting himself with his own words there..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "Ahem, I must admit that Jebrael's analysis did give me some inspirations..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "But! An outstanding researcher should be able to accept the opinion of others when they are correct. Needless obstinacy will make it impossible to make an academic breakthrough! Don't you think so too?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "You've said everything that can be said from either side. Is there even anything left for us to say?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "And here we see the researcher's ability to twist facts in its natural habitat..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "It's nothing of the sort! This is the deepening of understanding! *sigh* Your inability to realize that shows that you still have a long way to go."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Speaking of ways, is the place marked on the map our next destination?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "Yes, I think it's where all treasures meet, and all secrets end."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "Of course, it will be the end of our grand adventure too, and the penultimate chapter of my masterpiece!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "While I really wish to obtain all the answers at this instant, my body is exhausted..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Nachtigal and the others are still at the oasis... Oh, right, Samail's subordinates reported to him about merchants. Do you think they were attacked?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "Oh no! I almost forgot that!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jebrael",
                    "T": "I told them what to do if something like that happened, so they... should be fine."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Whoa! That's a first. Paimon's never heard Jebrael sound so uncertain."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hmm, let's get back to Nachtigal's group as soon as we can then. It'll be bad if they are in hot water that they can't get themselves out of!"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
