    "7305523": {
        "Desc": "Continue exploring",
        "Step": "Though Tirzad believes that King Deshret's throne must be located at a greater height that matches its hallowed position, it seems that the upward way must first take a downward turn...",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Yeah, we're obviously inside... But where's the throne?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "Why would you think the throne would be facing the entrance? It isn't a receptionist's desk. Hmm, actually, I feel like I shouldn't say such... Uh, disrespectful things in a place like this."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "Anyway, King Deshret's throne should be in a more \"dignified\" place, or in simpler terms, a place that's higher up."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jebrael",
                    "T": "The mechanisms here probably stopped working a long time ago. We've got to find a way to reactivate them."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Ooh... Paimon can't wait to see what the throne looks like."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Everything linked to King Deshret is huge! So that throne is definitely very, very huge, right? Hehe, Paimon wants to take a seat on it!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Benben",
                    "T": "Bee-eep? Beep..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Something seems to be the matter with Benben. It seems like... it wants to go down?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Huh? But Tirzad said the throne is definitely higher up..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "Hmm... to go up, we must first go down. You cannot reach a peak without falling to your lowest, just like..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Just like in life."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "Yes! Exactly! Hah, looks like you've learned quite a bit these past few days you spent with me, eh?"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
