    "7305525": {
        "Desc": "Activate Plinth(s) of the Secret Rites",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "...Oh, it's you. Is there anything else you want to discuss?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Let's talk about Jebrael."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "To think that I remained doubtful of him until the end. I'm such an awful person..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "Now, all I have for him is gratitude..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "I've never been able to commit before this, whether in academics or in life... But that ends now. I will take the path I believe in, no matter how difficult it may be..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "This is the least I can do to pay my respects to him..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I want to talk about King Deshret."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "To be honest, I'm starting to doubt the credibility of the articles I've read..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "That prayer... It gives me a strange feeling that I can't put a finger on. And Samail too... What he said... I think I should study it further once I get back."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "Of course, my main mission is still to write my paper like I originally planned."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Let's talk about Jeht for a moment."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "*sigh* I, too, wish that I could do something for her, but..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "I can't..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "And she refuses to say anything. If she would just speak her desire, I would be willing to do anything in my power to help her...!"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "7305526": {
        "Desc": "Continue forward",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Sorry... I'm still not very good at controlling my emotions."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Don't apologize."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Yeah... We know you're going through a tough time."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Thank you... May your travels be smooth."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Oh, Paimon hopes that everything will go well for you too... Paimon's sure it will!"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "7305527": {
        "Desc": "Activate the mechanism in the center of the hall",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Bonifaz",
                    "T": "Where are Omid and Mirsad? Are they..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nachtigal",
                    "T": "Don't worry. They're both fine. It's just that... they have other plans so they won't continue working with us."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Bonifaz",
                    "T": "Huh? What do we do? We can't handle all the work with only the two of us. We've gotta hire more people! But who'd want to come to Aaru Village..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Bonifaz",
                    "T": "Forget it, let's discuss this later. Anyway, Cyrus got back safely. That's at least something to be happy about, right? I'm never letting it go to such a dangerous place again."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nachtigal",
                    "T": "What are you talking about? We're Sumpter Beast merchants. What are we going to eat if our Sumpter Beasts don't work?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nachtigal",
                    "T": "You can't simply fill your belly with wind. Even if you could, open your mouth here, and I guarantee that you'll get a mouthful of sand instead..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Bonifaz",
                    "T": "But we can't let Cyrus take risks. You look pretty strong to me, so why don't you carry our goods instead?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nachtigal",
                    "T": "?"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
