    "7305508": {
        "Desc": "Return to Aaru Village",
        "Step": "Time to conclude this archaeological expedition... Return to Aaru Village to meet Bonifaz.",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Bonifaz",
                    "T": "To think that something like that happened... Anemo Archon bless us all..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Bonifaz",
                    "T": "*sigh* I'm really sorry about what happened to Jebrael. But at least all of you returned safely."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nachtigal",
                    "T": "I think we may have to reconsider our career as traveling merchants... The desert is a hundred times more dangerous than I expected... Even someone as capable as Jebrael..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nachtigal",
                    "T": "A nobody like me doesn't have that many lives! Ugh..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Bonifaz",
                    "T": "This may be bad timing, but I have to ask about what all of you plan to do now..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nachtigal",
                    "T": "I believe Tirzad will be returning to Sumeru City."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "...Me? Yes, I will. I—I should head back and start writing my paper."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "I must... record everything that I witnessed."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "But not for academic glory or anything... Jebrael did as he promised he would, yet I... I've always been avoiding my responsibilities."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "Now it's my turn. I too must shoulder my responsibilities..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "And as for this stone slate..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "I've prepared a replica for reference. As for the original... I hope you'll keep it safe for me. I'm not trying to run from danger! It's a commission, you hear it? A commission!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "Just think about it. I'll be completely occupied with my paper soon, but an adventurer like you will never stop adventuring, right?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "If you make new discoveries during this time... Wouldn't we make the perfect team? The thesis material shall be mine, and the Mora yours..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "That's perfect! We'll be making the best use of all our resources!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "And Jeht... What do you plan to do now? Do you have any friends you can rely on or something?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Father... He was so busy, he never had the time for anything... He didn't leave anything behind, just that axe he always used..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Father said he hoped he could meet her again in the Eternal Oasis... He said that day was still very, very far away... Liar! He lied to me, and to my mother..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "He should keep his own promise! Now I have to fulfill it for him, and... take his axe and mother's research notes, which he kept with his luggage..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "...To the Eternal Oasis. I hope they'll find true peace there."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Benben",
                    "T": "...Bee-eep!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Is there anything we can do to help?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Thank you, but... it's alright. While I was taking a quick look through my mother's research notes, I noticed what seemed like casual diary entries on the edges of the pages."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "I found out that my father is from this tribe called \"Tanit\"... So, I plan to look for them... Perhaps they can tell me about my father..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "Sorry, I just... I haven't... I'm sorry..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Let's give her a moment to herself."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Bonifaz",
                    "T": "Yeah... Anyway, Nachtigal and I will be staying here for a while."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nachtigal",
                    "T": "We'll think long and hard about our future..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "We should be staying in Sumeru for some time too... Paimon just has this feeling that there are so many more secrets to uncover."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Bonifaz",
                    "T": "Come to us if you need anything. We'll do our best to help you."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nachtigal",
                    "T": "And good luck in your adventures."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
