    "7305522": {
        "Desc": "",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "The door's closed again? Thank goodness, we made it out in time..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "Jebrael... protected us, but he... *sigh*"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeht",
                    "T": "*sob* Father..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Benben",
                    "T": "Beep... Beep-boop beep... Bee-eep..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "It must be Jebrael who opened the door for us. Without him, we would've been..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "He fulfilled his promise..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "This place may not be completely safe... Let's meet up with Nachtigal's group and head back to Aaru Village..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "???",
                    "T": "Refusing to give up, Jeht examined the entrance to Khaj-Nisut time after time, only to find the door tightly shut.\\nBehind it was dead silence. Things had happened and were beyond redemption.\\nJeht, now having but to accept reality, put away Jebrael's axe carefully. It is the only thing he has left behind.\\nWe finally managed to persuade her to come back with us to the camp. We then informed the merchants of what happened and returned to Aaru Village..."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "7305506": {
        "Desc": "",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Tirzad",
                    "T": "*cough* Nachtigal's invigorating drinks really are strong. If you sat me down at a table now, I'm certain I could write a million words in one go."
                }
            ]
        ]
    }
